import React from 'react';
import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from 'swiper/react';
import 'swiper/css';
import SwiperCore,
{
  Pagination,
  Navigation,
  Autoplay
} from 'swiper';

import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import CardMedia from '@mui/material/CardMedia';
import CardContent from '@mui/material/CardContent';
import Typography from '@mui/material/Typography';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';

import FavoriteBorderIcon from '@mui/icons-material/FavoriteBorder';


import { Button, CardActionArea, CardActions } from '@mui/material';

import fisrt_product from '../../assets/icons/images/image'
import second_product from '../../assets/images/image-slider/working-project-sl-2.png'

import './Sales.css';

// install Swiper modules

SwiperCore.use([Pagination, Navigation, Autoplay ]);

  return (
    <Swiper

        onSwiper={(swiper) => console.log(swiper)}

        //   "delay": 2500,
        //   "disableOnInteraction": false
        // }}

        breakpoints={{

            "slidesPerView": 1,
            "spaceBetween": 10

          "640": {
            "slidesPerView": 2,
            "spaceBetween": 20
          },
          "768": {
            "slidesPerView":4,

    >
      <SwiperSlide>

                Vermivet Solución Oral 1l

                Antiparasitario Interno, recomendado para aves, bovino y porcino.
              </Typography>
            </CardContent>

      </SwiperSlide>
      <SwiperSlide>
        <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 345 }}>

            />

export default Carousel;
